# Daily Leads Feature — Implementation Plan

This document outlines the technical architecture, UI/UX placement, API design, error handling logic, and the exact files to be updated for the "Daily Leads Simple Version".

## 1. Mapped Codebase Files

### New Files to Create:
- `migrations/032_daily_leads.sql` - Database schema (Tables: `daily_posts`, `smart_links`, `post_generations_quota`, storage: `daily-post-images`).
- `app/api/daily-leads/generate/route.js` - Main AI generation backend edge function.
- `app/api/smart-links/create/route.js` - Endpoint to shorten URLs and generate hashes.
- `app/l/[hash]/route.js` - Public redirection and click-tracking API route.
- `app/dashboard/daily-leads/page.jsx` - The main Daily Leads dashboard page.
- `components/dashboard/daily-leads/GeneratorView.jsx` - The split-pane AI generator UI component.
- `components/dashboard/daily-leads/TopMetrics.jsx` - The summary statistics bar.
- `components/dashboard/daily-leads/HistoryList.jsx` - The past posts table.

### Existing Files to Modify:
- [store/full_project_context.md.resolved](file:///c:/Users/Waris%20Rawa/Desktop/ai-marketing-automation/store/full_project_context.md.resolved) - Update with new tables and API routes once finalized.
- `components/Sidebar.jsx` (or the equivalent Dashboard navigation component) - To add the link to `/dashboard/daily-leads`.

